title: Whatever Happened to Baby Jane?
description:
Year: 1962 
Running Time: 133 min. 
Director: Robert Aldrich 
Cast: Bette Davis, Joan Crawford, Victor Buono, Maidie Norman, Anna Lee 

Genre: Drama 
Two aging film actresses live as virtual recluses in an old Hollywood mansion. Jane Hudson, a successful child star, cares for her crippled sister Blanche, who&#039;s career in later years eclipsed that of Jane. Now the two live together, their relationship affected by simmering subconscious thoughts of mutual envy, hate and revenge.
